omy","date":"2024-12-10","headline":"Mori Memorial Foundation releases GPCI 2024 report for 48 major cities, includes 'GPCI–Financial Centers' index for the 2nd time.","id":"f72bd50d-351a-43c3-b92b-76273beaa194","is_major":false,"source":"Business Wire","source_type":"news","summary":"In Tokyo, the Mori Memorial Foundation’s Institute for Urban Strategies, founded by Mori Building, a prominent developer, unveiled the Global Power City Index (GPCI) 2024 report evaluating the competitiveness of 48 global cities. A new addition to the report is the 'GPCI–Financial Centers' index, emphasizing initiatives cities are taking to bolster their global financial standing. This index complements the main report, providing a comprehensive overview of each city's strengths. The GPCI serves as a significant tool for analyzing urban performance and international status in the modern era.","tickers":[],"time":"03:02:14","timestamp":"2024-12-10T03:02:14Z","url":"http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20241209714811/en/Mori-Memorial-Foundation-Issues-GPCI%E2%80%932024-and-GPCI%E2%80%93Financial-Centers-Reports/?feedref=JjAwJuNHiystnCoBq_hl-bsjWlVyeNLyq_m2tvaHJJaD1w08bW43U_zsPK9s38B4rCOi9QzgjCezTS3Nw_X6kJUrpSBm-Hav1w-UkdSlG3miu0ZZ-LtXjCwD3Ec3ldN_zZCGORvG0LE20YOvo49uqw=="},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"investing","date":"2024-12-10","headline":"China's Imports Increase by 2.4% Year on Year in Yuan Terms from Jan-Nov","id":"2154ee48-c23d-4265-b955-dc5e27d85d3c","is_major":true,"source":"Tradex","source_type":"news","summary":null,"tickers":[],"time":"03:02:01","timestamp":"2024-12-10T03:02:01Z","url":null},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"investing","date":"2024-12-10","headline":"China's January to November Exports Rise 5.4% Year on Year in USD Terms","id":"dccfd628-4963-4785-a625-7c7a498c4f54","is_major":true,"source":"Tradex","source_type":"news","summary":null,"tickers":[],"time":"03:01:01","timestamp":"2024-12-10T03:01:01Z","url":null},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"investing